              WhatsApp, Telegram, email, and web push notifications within 5 minutes of status change
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white border border-green-200 p-6 rounded-lg text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <i data-lucide="smartphone" class="w-8 h-8 text-green-600"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">Mobile Dashboard</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Real-time status, historical data, and settings management from any device
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white border border-green-200 p-6 rounded-lg text-center">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
              <i data-lucide="trending-up" class="w-8 h-8 text-green-600"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">Revenue Protection</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              Prevent $70-200+ daily losses by catching closures within minutes, not hours
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="py-20 px-4 bg-green-600">
